Ònyeisi ụka Katolic n’ụwa bụ Popu Francis eyipụla otu ụkọchukwu akwa ụkọchukwu ya maka ịmụta nwa nwoke gbara afọ 10.
Wenceslas Munyeshyaka, gbara afọ  64, onye Rwanda arụọla ọrụ dịka ụkọchụkwụ na Fransị afọ iri atọ.
Ozi na-efesa n’intanet nke Bishopụ Evrex binyere aka kwuru na “anapụla ya ikike ịbụ ụkọchukwụ nakwa ime ihe ọbụla dịka ụkọchukwu.”
Owo Church Attacks: Ihe onyonyo etu e si lie ndị e gburu n'ụka Katọlik dị n'Owo Ondo Steeti17 Juun 2022

Ụlọọrụ Dayọsis Evreux gwara BBC na ozi ahụ na-efegharị bụ eziokwu dịka ọ gbadoro ụkwụ na iwu nke Popu nyere n’ọnwa Maachị, afọ 2023.
Munyeshyaka,onye si mba Rwanda gbaa ọsọ ndụ oge ọgụ mkpochapụ agbụrụ na Rwanda n’afọ 1994 ekwubeghị ihe ọbụla maka ihe mere.
A kwụsịrị ya ọrụ n’ike n’ọnwa Disemba afọ 2021 dịka o kwetara na ya bụ nna mụrụ nwa gbara afọ 10.
Ụka Katọlik anaghị enye ndị ụkọchukwu ha ohere ịlụnwaanyị maọbụ buta nwa.
E chiri Munyeshyaka Fada na Rwanda n’afọ 1992 bụ ebe e boro ya ebubo na aka ya dị n’ogbugbu narị kwuru nari ndị Tutsi gbatara ọsọ ndụ n’ụlọụka ya na Kigali oge ọgụ mkpochapụ agbụrụ.
